title: The Complete Tutankhamun-The King, the Tomb, the Royal Treasure
description:
The Complete Tutankhamun: The King, the Tomb, the Royal Treasure
Thames and Hudson | 1990 | 0500050589 | English | 228 pages | PDF | 30 MB

Provides insights into the discovery, excavation, and analysis of the tomb and its treasures. Written by one of the world's leading scholars of the period, and illustrations with specially commissioned diagrams, charts, and photographs, it is essential reading for everyone interest in ancient Egypt
